summary:
This Mod Adds A New (Female Only) Light Armor Set, A New Dagger And A New Sword To Skyrim.
For CBBE, UNP, UNPB, CBBE BodySlide & CB++, other body types are available but may not be up-to date or supported at the moment, this includes... SeveNBase Bombshell

Meshes by SkyrimForDaWin
Textures by Reaper9111
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=5][center]This mod is now being updated and maintained on its new page:
 [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85188/?]Unclaimed Delivery The Second Shipment[/url]
Go check it out!





Now Available [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/8646/?]Unclaimed Delivery for Skyrim SE[/url]

Pictures of the ground items and the armor/weapon stats are at the bottom of this page.[/center][/size][/b]

[b][size=5][center]Currently, the armor is for CBBE, UNP, UNPB, CBBE BodySlide & CB++, the following are available but may not be up-to date or supported at the moment... SeveNBase Bombshell...

Please read the installation instructions before installing the mod.[/center][/size][/b]

[center][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37541/][b][size=3]Italian translation[/size][/b][/url] by: Davieon[/center]


[b][size=5][center]DESCRIPTION[/center][/size][/b]
[center]This mod adds a crate to the Riverwood Trader in Riverwood, addressed to Ingrid of Helgen. I don't think I need to explain why the crate was not delivered. Inside the crate is a set of "Refined Leather Armor" (Female only), 2 "Eviscerator" daggers and (as of Version 1.2.0+) a long and short version of a new sword that I have named "Brutal Eviscerator".
On top of the crate is a Note, which when carried will reveal the armor and weapons in the crafting list at the forge under leather (armor) and steel (weapons).

The Armor set is a Mash-Up of Skyrim assets with a few custom Meshes made by myself, the Eviscerator Weapons are made from scratch by myself and both the armor set and the weapons have custom textures made by my friend Reaper9111.
Don't forget to endorse if you like the mod & feel free to upload some screenshots.[/center]


[b][size=5][center]Special Install/Uninstall Info[/center][/size][/b]

[center]The CB++ patch will require you to have installed CB++ as per the instructions on the mod page (link below)[/center]
[center][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32731/][b][size=3]Bodyslide CB Plus Plus[/size][/b][/url] by: ChronoTrigger77[/center]


[center]The CBBE BodySlide patch will require CBBE BodySlide to be installed as per the instructions on the mod page (link below)[/center]
[center][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666/][b][size=3]Caliente's Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition[/size][/b][/url] by: Caliente[/center]

[center]The SeveNBase Bombshell version will require the animations and skeleton(s) mentioned on the body's mod page to be installed for it to work (link below)[/center]
[center][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36992/][b][size=3]SeveNBase custom female body replacer[/size][/b][/url] by: Crosscrusade DeMoNhUnTeR1986 Sevennity[/center]

[center]Please make sure the appropriate mod(s) are installed correctly before attempting to install the BodySlide versions of this mod.[/center]


[b][size=5][center]Install/Uninstall Info[/center][/size][/b]
[center]Install
Install using NMM

Manual Install
-Download manualy
-Open archive with 7Zip (or similar)
-Extract the files to your skyrim directory
- activate the ESP in the Skyrim Launcher

Manual Uninstall
-remove the following files from your skyrim directory
skyrimDatameshesSkyMeshesUnlcaimed Delivery
skyrimDatatexturesSkyTexturesUnlcaimed Delivery
SkyrimDataThe Unclaimed Delivery.ESP[/center]
